cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.HC 

This paper deals with the problem of automatic parsing of floorplan images using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also presents a novel dataset and an improved multi-task convolutional neural network, which falls under the categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the annotations of the dataset, which involves the use of polygons, which could be categorized under cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the paper discusses the potential applications of the research in the field of augmented and virtual reality, which could be categorized under cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
